nk"&gt;传统的、令人印象深刻的演员选择&lt;/a&gt;，其中许多新面孔和声音可能只有当地杂货店的邻居才能认出。至少有一项&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/e6DxN1_dHXn3Fk2hsKrh1kw4B_1-UHDgfgd1nnG8O-roxlPO-SyYsUHew1kStHyFhkmaWHN1FiZ64Mhsp0GA74JGj_CrF4rEYAQdULwdgOMBZD3uyKkv52GaXuCl2XjzuRB4PiyS5CBXr8xoEsn3Cny7yYYLmHA-l9_yUk1cWnLV-qO5d-_kGuKTW_i-PODNr7IT3QCoBndx3tqZo4aRAkSiWbiT100AO7R2mpI32KiielYx8-WFlggno2mUFmXYd-kyM0iqOSydR7fjgc8K5NFfQR0PR9YmxOoM_BHzKXfmXKrp-Q6T3GjUqOuobjnTxcQoWOdbFXvZynMKn4iwp-_lLiwPsg0IVD5IUFOhCW9zd3t_GI1ApX8DL1M/vl9zNjDIYjbT4iAqhaEv94rpvVcLbkv2/18" target="_blank"&gt;无人预见到的&lt;/a&gt;重大商业成功。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;尽管如此，庆祝活动仍笼罩着一层阴郁的气氛&lt;/strong&gt;。裁员、产量减少和票房下滑，让这个曾经定义美国文化力量的行业的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ZniealaNcFMm7sLHN2mVeZbpGFbdK-ouiSeAruzcovABbHq2d22KDGF6xumhpCRr_kKOxno7daImbSwr_Uje231yBUutr3tIZ0AFgKK3dwGg8SqpdCKY6xB6Qu_Bnuj0WPEgSwPHpqbvGK3TN61Dkp3Pt4m1ddnOalXT19Rr4DsRH6s8ZHkNl0n4yNaZUaITIUhXEtSIzRhLDM32uuti0pJ_o6kUxc9iwATyzZorMbDmdkCXqCieVjOhOHFrWQnw1CKRIIkckQvEOx-JqNj2HANIBODjTE2iuPueEAm9AuBExTuwP_2Q5uN7LB6zcH_I_BPN59SQv9bdVRu0XCJC0ZaqDgMsNFC7JcYyAG9SaTQE8lGm_F4TK7oun4M/Yl00MfOW1kOoKPEKAQG9QQ09AXbq8CB7/18" target="_blank"&gt;气氛变得黯淡&lt;/a&gt;。好莱坞只是在衰落，还是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/536Jwej_Qt1bZQqOehM1gSho8Y8RKc-27xlQiDPkdBl3tihWBwwjyyDs09E1U4RDKkTl59W-uExJriP70pi2Aes03Ut3pFb1VtTITrhfp6agU8UMD15eWMtP8_6o7ihgfiUH4pmUVmNFsjG_FPvfpXTiS8SNwag9VyJL2mVZczAnbnZjj17xYZeLEr48tKYaVs-rJJHsgEQAFAQu1epg0WRinzqh2RKUIIsqQItstcOheX7F1u-pEszjfZS3liKJAJUFfK4etXEaJtWLlIlUI-7dBLr12WRDnvd7GuButle4dLTvX3npVppISO3Vpp8qA2IYfyvI4zbHC59vwV2olVPvvcOpOy_gS1KXhw5WO-NbKOlZr-WTkoMRb-Y/d127cIs4bt-oSUBniB8CsceTbiTYS5YY/18" target="_blank"&gt;濒临灭绝&lt;/a&gt;？&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;伊朗传奇导演&lt;/strong&gt;贾法尔·帕纳西 (Jafar Panahi) 忙着忙于忙于接受有关他最新电影《&lt;em&gt;这只是一次意外&lt;/em&gt;》(It 