0px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;每日图表&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iB2JsvU7DRvY/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iB2JsvU7DRvY/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;中国又派出了至少五架解放军飞机进入台湾附近的敏感地区，此前中国曾在没有任何解释的情况下短暂推迟了航班。多年来，北京一直派遣飞机环岛飞行，作为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/O1Y3qMNraDUJuNolqiX8V_o3N39wtQFIU4Bjff0HFOMYn0flLn6uMbRIq1IU9e_yxJMPQrYdclT01oLjD3IIBuopBawJ4ebuuS19GpeH2kIG95tsgqJgjc_g0Q3jPrQq0m9NWCfUtHi2YpGx_s7WmHUUusAt3-dwFYeBGdzNiN8gJjsjeCiiiHGfkKP17ZcB1CwMmaEK39ZDc8BS0nOdiIuC5gSjYb4VG09YV4e91r0ABUz1hDm-XFIp9ThdBKxUbf_-PjQ310tiEkYqwuDYCOJAzzY_j9lCT9M98XRTIcKyUtKAJQRwIZWeh8Q_vw51M2z-BTpGJ-1z-0HkjGKcYBFO3f5i27mcdOXrw5_EJNJJ7WpI6R7qGauNJ20WDA_30PfswmMwkFnJ74kzv5ieoNwz5g30VjYMmpb9Ky9zWfsCV9RpwpGQ0qWtFDAos1hUhyPmpfaChtjBiS3NzL0_dfm6dtJWY3JXxSoFlxTr2h-1IGWfTTnbZftmOFPfMjiUcZaqAwYUkuGNpTDw/u-QqkmlAgGvMIWfyziI3mmhujWK83UcH/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="在不明原因的平静之后，中国向台湾派遣了更多战机"&gt;施压策略&lt;/a&gt;，习近平上个月在两国领导人预计几周后会晤之前告诉特朗普，中国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/a5CgyhRE9Q02qCigRDLVHeOWv_FtuV_pryKhyLM38_KXRQqQHE1ADb0P9maDZkAPqx5g7zNYGgB_lzTdg1JDEnJPLz-lcJyQiE1kKmdUWucKBEeMucLpNxNXfMPN45XBjBtYsld2rJpwsKec4m7do0cYiSmlZ3khJ9ha1bfj5HQajxO7i_xcKkfwnVtTWjzDue0litS5XIu5AWZIJHWHsNwL199uJuv-_UD174qWIriHwLuEd8E0va43jHxKiVRofcA6XKimC567uhb5Iy7m_EY-miGXB75fCSHkXAUVnrXofYxsKQkbOW8At01p0zQR-QZEW1